Title: 70.3 RP 15min reps over rolling hills

CoachComments: Focus for the efforts is to dial in your 70.3 RP and work on smooth and steady pedal stroke. Make sure you stay seated and aero, keep your upper body still and relaxed. Drive from your glutes.
